headline.main: SCREEN SCENES FROM A LOCAL VANTAGE POINT

results.lead_paragraph: CREDIT the Soviet Union's film-makers with setting a precedent. Hollywood's intrepid "explorers" already have ascended to the moon, descended 20,000 leagues under the sea and journeyed to the center of the earth but the Russians now are orbiting the sun on their movie screens and may be doing the same in American theatres in the near future.
